{"lemma":"صَفَرَ","slug":"صَفَرَ","root":"ص.ف.ر","root_slug":"ص-ف-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ف-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"صَفَرَ","root":"صفر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":11,"pos_tags":["adj","name","noun","num","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":19},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24452"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"name","gloss":"Safar (the second month of the Islamic calendar)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be empty, to be devoid, to be vacant"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to empty, to void, to vacate, to evacuate, to free"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"empty, void, devoid, free from"},{"pos":"num","gloss":"zero","examples":[{"text":"Next: واحد, or ١ = 1"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to dye yellow, to make yellow, to color yellow"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"brass"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"money"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of صَفِرَ (ṣafira) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"jaundice"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"plural of أَصْفَر (ʔaṣfar, “yellow”)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to whistle"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to hiss"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to chirp, to stridulate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to scream (of a siren)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to whistle"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to hiss"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to chirp, to stridulate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to scream (of a siren)"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From ص ف ر (ṣ f r, “void”), supposedly because pagan Arabs looted during this month and left the houses empty.\n\nSemantic loan from Sanskrit शून्य (śūnya), also with the original meaning of “empty, void”. Compare صَفْر (ṣafr, “empty, void”) (also صِفْر (ṣifr)).\n\nCausative from the root ص ف ر (ṣ f r), from which the color or defect adjective أَصْفَر (ʔaṣfar, “yellow”) also comes.\n\nRelated to أَصْفَر (ʔaṣfar, “yellow”), from the root ص ف ر (ṣ f r).\n\nIn its meaning \"jaundice\", related to أَصْفَر (ʔaṣfar, “yellow”), from the root ص ف ر (ṣ f r).\n\nInflected form.\n\nPresumably, originally an intensive of صَفَرَ (ṣafara, “to whistle, hiss, chirp”), later losing its intensive sense."},"ipa":["/sˤa.far/","/sˤifr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24452","headword_ar":"صَفَرَ","root":"Sfr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafiyrN","text_ar":"صَفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,) with which ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SufaArN","text_ar":"صُفَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. in a phrase mentioned below; (S;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sf~r","text_ar":"صفّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taSofiyrN","text_ar":"تَصْفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a bird, a vulture, S, and a serpent, or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asowad","text_ar":"اَسْوَد"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoraj","text_ar":"اَعْرَج"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aibon qitorap","text_ar":"اِبْن قِتْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSalap","text_ar":"اَصَلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whistled;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mkaA","text_ar":"مكَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uttered, a certain sound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, * K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without the utterance of letters."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) [It is mostly said of a bird: see an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaw~N","text_ar":"جَوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] One says [also],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safara","text_ar":"صَفَرَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY AlS~af~aArapi","text_ar":"فِى الصَّفَّارَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He whistled in the whistle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safara biAloHimaAri","text_ar":"صَفَرَ بِالْحِمَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sf~r","text_ar":"صفّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He called the ass to water"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by whistling;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for to do thus is the common custom of the Arabs]. (M, K.) And Fr mentions the phrase, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna fiY kalaAmihi SafaArN","text_ar":"كَانَ فِى كَلَامِهِ صَفَارٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafiyrN","text_ar":"صَفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There was in his speech a whistling"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safira","text_ar":"صَفِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafarN","text_ar":"صَفَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, K, &c.) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SufuwrN","text_ar":"صُفُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) and accord. to the T,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safara","text_ar":"صَفَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SufuwrapN","text_ar":"صُفُورَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, empty, void,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vacant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K;) namely, a house or tent; (S;) or a vessel, (S, M, &c.,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlT~aEaAmi waAl$~araAbi","text_ar":"مِنَ الطَّعَامِ وَالشَّرَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of food and beverage"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and a skin,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina All~abani","text_ar":"مِنَ اللَّبَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;) and a hand; (A;) and a thing; (S, M;) and accord. to ISk,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safira","text_ar":"صَفِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafiyrN","text_ar":"صَفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is said of a man. (TA.) [See also 4, last sentence but one.] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEuw*u biAll~`hi mino qaraEi AlfinaA='i waSafari","text_ar":"نَعُوذُ بِاللّٰهِ مِنْ قَرَعِ الفِنَا=ءِ وَصَفَرِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_inaA='i","text_ar":"الاـِنَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We seek preservation by God from the yard's becoming void of cattle, and the vessel's becoming empty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the perishing of the cattle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safirato wiTaAbuhu","text_ar":"صَفِرَتْ وِطَابُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, A, K, [in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waToAatuhu","text_ar":"وَطْاَتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Safira A_inaAw^uhu","text_ar":"صَفِرَ اـِنَاوُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A,) [lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His milk-skins,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his vessel, became empty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he died;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he perished."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A. [See also other explanations in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wTb","text_ar":"وطب"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sufira","text_ar":"صُفِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaforN","text_ar":"صَفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SufaAr","text_ar":"صُفَار"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yellow water in his belly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K","A"]}]}}